        "text": "\"The statement, signed by J. Stewart Williams, professor of geology, Utah State\nAgricultural College, Lincoln La Paz, director, Institute of Meteoritics, Uni-\nversity of New Mexico and Clyde T. Hardy, USAC geology professor read:"
